===Noun phrase===
'''Ancient Greek'''

The Greek language from the earliest records (Linear B inscriptions, 1700-1300 BCE) to about 300 BCE, including the main dialects [[Aeolic]], [[Arcadic]], [[Doric]], and [[Ionic]].

